videos.description: Georgia's Yante Maten draws contact with Alabama's Braxton Key and uses the give-and-go to perfection to finish with a dunk.
videos.headline: Maten bullies Alabama to get basket

videos.description: Alabama's Collin Sexton keeps the Crimson Tide's offense rolling by scoring their first seven points of the game against Georgia.
videos.headline: Sexton scores first seven points for the Tide

videos.description: Georgia's Derek Ogbeida swoops in for the putback dunk off Jordan Harris' missed 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Ogbeide flies in for the dunk

videos.description: Georgia's Yante Maten shows off his range by draining a deep 3-pointer against Alabama.
videos.headline: Maten hits deep 3

videos.description: Alabama's Collin Sexton draws the foul after putting Georgia's William Jackson II on skates en route to the basket.
videos.headline: Sexton makes Georgia dance

videos.description: Jordan Harris knocks down the corner 3-pointer off the great ball movement, giving the Bulldogs their sixth bucket in the first half from beyond the arc.
videos.headline: Georgia continues dominance from long range
